  "content": "<p></p><h1 class=\"title\"><img src=\"http://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px\" title=\"PFS Legal\" /> Bergelmir</h1><h2><b>Mother of Memories</b></h2><b>Source</b> <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://paizo.com/products/btpy94wj?Pathfinder-Campaign-Setting-Inner-Sea-Gods-Hardcover\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Inner Sea Gods pg. 324</i></a><br /><b>Pathfinder Wiki</b> <a href=\"http://www.pathfinderwiki.com/wiki/Bergelmir\">Bergelmir</a><p></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Details</h3><p><b>Alignment</b> CG<br /><b>Pantheon</b> Giant Deities<br /><b>Areas of Concern</b> Elders, family, genealogy<br /><b>Domains</b> <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Chaos\">Chaos</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Community\">Community</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Good\">Good</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Knowledge\">Knowledge</a><br /><b>Subdomains</b> <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Repose\">Ancestors</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Community\">Education (Community)</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Knowledge\">Education (Knowledge)</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Community\">Family</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Community\">Home</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Knowledge\">Memory</a><br /><i>* Requires the <u><a href=\"TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Acolyte%20of%20Apocrypha\">Acolyte of Apocrypha</a></u> trait.</i><br /><b>Favored Weapon</b> Quarterstaff<br /><b>Symbol</b> Three bolts of lightning<br /><b>Sacred Animal(s)</b> Sea turtle<br /><b>Sacred Color(s)</b> Gray, white<br /><br /><br /></p><div style=\"position:relative;left:0%;border:2px ridge #434343;width:100%;height:100%\"><div class=\"wiki-content-full\"><iframe style=\"overflow-y:hidden;width:100%;height:450px\" src=\"https://pathfinderwiki.com/wiki/Bergelmir\"> </iframe></div>\n </div>",
